sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM user_contributions 
WHERE user_id = (SELECT artist_id FROM artists WHERE artist_name = 'Taylor Swift');

SELECT user_name
FROM users
WHERE user_id NOT IN (SELECT user_id FROM user_contributions);

SELECT artist_name
FROM artists
WHERE artist_id = (
    SELECT artist_id
    FROM albums
    WHERE total_tracks = (
        SELECT MAX(total_tracks)
        FROM albums
    )
);

external_knowledge:
- "maestros" refers to artists;
- "performances on stage" metaphorically represent track appearances;
- "weaving their melodies across a vast tapestry of albums and their variations" indicates the tracks are spread across different albums and their versions;
- "top-five" implies the limit of 5 results after sorting in descending order.
